paragraphs.text:
import sqlc.implicits._

for(i <- 0 to (s.length -1)){
    val y = Array("Test", i, "t").mkString
    val hello = s(i).toJSON.toDF.withColumn("id", when($"_1"==="sup", y).otherwise(y))
    def aggConcat(col: String) = hello
      .map(row => (row.getAs[String]("id"), row.getAs[String](col)))
      .aggregateByKey(Vector[String]())(_ :+ _, _ ++ _)
      
    val result = aggConcat("_1").toDF.withColumn("_2", concat_ws(";", $"_2"))
    
    val sup = result.rdd.map(x => "\\[|\\]".r.replaceAllIn(x.toString, "").split("t,")).map(x=> (x(0), x(1)))
    sc.toRedisKV(sup, (6379))
}
